THE SQUIRRELMAIL TEAM
=====================

The SquirrelMail Project thanks each and every one that have made SquirrelMail
what it is today. This includes, but isn't limited to, bug reporters, patch
submitters, testers, plugin authors, community members, and many, many other.

The list below contains some of persons that have helped the project, with the
aim to give credit where it is due. If you feel that your name has wrongfully
been left out, please contact the SquirrelMail Project.

Main developers:
----------------
Alex Lemaresquier    <alex@brainstorm.fr>
Alexandros Vellis    <avel+sqm@noc.uoa.gr>          http://users.uoa.gr/~avel
Chris Hilts          <tassium@squirrelmail.org>     http://www.birdbrained.org
Fredrik Jervfors     <jervfors@squirrelmail.org>    http://fredrik.jervfors.se
Jonathan Angliss     <jon@squirrelmail.org>
Paul Lesniewski      <paul@squirrelmail.org>
Steve Brown          <sbrown25@gmail.com>
Thijs Kinkhorst      <kink@squirrelmail.org>        http://thijs.kinkhorst.nl

